<div  class='hr av-kia2kk5l-9a9617a39105f01ec07e16971b5062c1 hr-custom  avia-builder-el-6  el_after_av_image  el_before_av_textblock  hr-center hr-icon-no'><span class='hr-inner inner-border-av-border-fat'><span class="hr-inner-style"></span></span></div>
<section  class='av_textblock_section av-kia1lgvx-a287064e3d84bbc9d2b1a90bdcf0031b '   itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock'  itemprop="text" ><p style="text-align: center;">Since its inception in 1997, AKILA Group has established itself as <b>expert importers, packers and distributors of food products</b> in South Africa and a leading commodity trader globally. AKILA’s <b>wide</b> range of products includes <b>rice, sugar, beans, lentils, peas and more.</b></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">We have a global presence with operations in five countries across four continents, which allows us to manage our own procurement. This enables us to maintain the highest standards of quality. Our experts around the world test our products at the source, which means that we aim to bring you the world’s best.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Our name says it best: “AKILA”, which means “intelligent” or “wise”, is your assurance that you can always serve our products with confidence.</p>
</div></section></div><div  class='flex_column av-21qen-ccd6520323b263398cc1f94bad4ed5cb av_one_fifth  avia-builder-el-8  el_after_av_one_full  el_before_av_three_fifth  first flex_column_div av-zero-column-padding  column-top-margin'     ></div><div  class='flex_column av-1q84r-033bc1cc914b13784b1d26a63486c175 av_three_fifth  avia-builder-el-9  el_after_av_one_fifth  el_before_av_one_fifth  flex_column_div av-animated-generic bottom-to-top av-zero-column-padding  column-top-margin'     ><section  class='av_textblock_section av-kia1lgvx-1-fa9b27fccb5a1cd0c4005f82ba7e90f5 '   itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock av_inherit_color'  itemprop="text" ><p style="text-align: center;"><em>Our name says it best: “AKILA”, which means “intelligent” or “wise”, is your assurance that you can always serve our products with confidence.</em></p>
</div></section></div><div  class='flex_column av-1248b-0ae24b61a80c9036dcb0b33600a662e1 av_one_fifth  avia-builder-el-11  el_after_av_three_fifth  avia-builder-el-last  flex_column_div av-zero-column-padding  column-top-margin'     ></div></div></div></div><!-- close content main div --></div></div><div id='av_section_3'  class='avia-section av-kia2ixi2-af7184b71c73bc8670ce71e738c9505b main_color avia-section-default avia-no-border-styling  avia-builder-el-12  el_after_av_section  el_before_av_slideshow_full  avia-bg-style-scroll container_wrap fullsize'  ><div class='container av-section-cont-open' ><div class='template-page content  av-content-full alpha units'><div class='post-entry post-entry-type-page post-entry-11'><div class='entry-content-wrapper clearfix'>
